  "title": "BiquadEffect",
  "description": "Native biquad filter effect backed by a single `BiquadFilterNode` — the most common audio-shaping need, covering `lowpass` / `highpass` / `bandpass` / `notch` / `peaking` / `lowshelf` / `highshelf` / `allpass` via one `type` parameter. Insert it on an AudioBus (`bus.addEffect`) or a Voice (`voice.addEffect`). The single node serves as both inputNode and outputNode.",
